程序包 GeDBIT.dist

  • 接口概要 
    接口 说明
    Metric
    Metric is a distance oracle.
    WeightMatrix
    A WeightMatrix is the substitution matrix of an Alphabet of Symbol objects.
  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    CountedMetric
    Wrapper around a base Metric that counts the invocations of Metric.getDistance(IndexObject,IndexObject).
    EditDistance
    This class computes edit distance between two Strings.
    ImageMetric
    Computes the distance between images.
    LMetric
    This class computes the L family distance function on two vectors.
    MSMetric
    MSDataMetric implements the Metric interface.
    MSMSConstants
    Constant static default values for building indices on mass spectrometer data Code uses these as default, "tolerance" etc. also configurable via constructors.
    MSMSMetric
    MSMSMetric is an implementation of a fuzzy cosine distance metric for comparing tandem spectra signatures.
    SequenceFragmentMetric
    Computes distance on two Fragments.
    SymmetricSubstitutionWeightMatrix
    Implements a WeightMatrix by providing a symmetric substitution matrix of double distances for a given Alphabet.
    WHDGlobalFragmentMetric
    This class computes global alignment with weighted Hamming distance
    WHDGlobalSequenceFragmentMetric
    Computes global alignment on Fragments with Weighted Hamming Distance
